er how my day went, I had this little one smiling back at me.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my day\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kids remind you of what's really important.\\\"\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Armstrong (no relation to Lance Armstrong) has competed as a cyclist in four different Olympic games beginning in 2004 in Athens, followed by Beijing, London, and Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.583910573147898e-38, \"text\": \"Lance Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8086545725164627, \"rank\": 0.23662181598356935, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9984083965559609, \"rank\": 0.0015941343584057834, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999964648578684, \"rank\": 2.548099784019961e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"h