 \"Armstrong\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"my secret weapon\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"a good or bad day\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not really care how my bike ride went.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my bike ride\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so it really put things in perspective and so the stress and all that I put into the bike each and every day when I did not have Lucas, it kind of just wore on me and it really just hung until my next ride.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"score\": 0.7097299932115503, \"rank\": 0.40362439602328853, \"text\": \"Lucas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1971}, {\"ngram\": \"the stress\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"my next ride\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when you show up and you have this little human being and you love him so much\\u2026 all of that goes away until your next ride and it's gonna be better because that's just a small part of your life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this little human being\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"your next ride\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"just a small part\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to being an Olympic gold medalist and mom, Armstrong is also a business owner.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.753124213504674e-16, \"text\": \"Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"mom\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"a business owner\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She opened Pivot Lifestyle + Fitness centers in Idaho to help other people have the opportunity to keep moving and be active so they can live their best lives.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2480, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idaho\", \"score\": 0.9976587036582929, \"rank\": 0.00214841771915896, \"text\": \"Idaho\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idaho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Idaho\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pivot Lifestyle + Fitness centers\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"their best lives\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[Editor's note: This story originally was published byLive Action News.]\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"[Editor's note\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"This story\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"Action News\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SUPPORT TRUTHF